FBIS3-44046 "drafr015_c_94002" FBIS-AFR-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Travel Warning Issued MB2301080994 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0743 GMT 23 Jan 94 MB2301080994 Johannesburg SAPA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pretoria Jan 23 SAPA -- Minister of Foreign Affairs Pik Botha on Sunday requested South Africans not to travel to Maseru or its surrounding areas because of the fighting that broke out there in the morning. "South Africans are requested not to travel to maseru and its environs until the situation has returned to normal," he said in Pretoria.
